{"tid":1625323,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"以抗爭為本的在家健身資訊Youtube頻道","createTime":"2019-10-05T06:34:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T06:30:44.000Z","uid":222189,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"d48bf0d01504ef9643cbe5459860b33232340215","tid":1625323,"uid":222189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:34:31.000Z","msg":"舊POST問過有冇人想要影片黎集合健身資訊<br />\n以抗爭為出發點係屋企用最低資源提升身體能力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1615567/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1615567/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n依家出第一條片，已經整緊第二條<br />\n頭兩條都應該係口水片冇野睇，講觀念，聽聲就得。<br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位手足幫我睇下會唔會太細聲？我講野會唔會太口齒不清？一條片會唔會太長要斬返開？<br />\n<br />\n覺得有用請比戰友們，不分位置，因為我相信位置係流動既，抗爭係長久既。<br />\n<br />\n有咩唔明請問，講錯左請屌<br />\n<br />\n一得閒就整，返工忙就唔整。可能一日一條片亦可能成星期冇片出，我都唔知。<br />\n總之盡快。<br />\n<br />\n第一集講緊 點解要做尖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b954326ce5d5c1be1e38e0f88ba33a4c701137","tid":1625323,"uid":176282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:35:14.000Z","msg":"thanks<br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"32223762b9ed608e977158718b444fd030075696","tid":1625323,"uid":222189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76b954326ce5d5c1be1e38e0f88ba33a4c701137","tid":1625323,"uid":176282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:35:14.000Z","msg":"thanks<br />\n<br />\n推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:37:07.000Z","msg":"多謝 巴打幫手睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c34116dfa592dff1db9fe985cf4fa5ff9dd9aee1","tid":1625323,"uid":321913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:37:37.000Z","msg":"［裝修指南］維港沿岸篇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624936</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"de194e42ee1f436e3ecacea43d8f7d76b78bfe00","tid":1625323,"uid":176282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32223762b9ed608e977158718b444fd030075696","tid":1625323,"uid":222189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76b954326ce5d5c1be1e38e0f88ba33a4c701137","tid":1625323,"uid":176282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:35:14.000Z","msg":"thanks<br />\n<br />\n推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:37:07.000Z","msg":"多謝 巴打幫手睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:38:33.000Z","msg":"睇緊，推"},{"pid":"fcab41705b9831525395167ad215c0d9dbbfe259","tid":1625323,"uid":299255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:39:34.000Z","msg":"未睇,sub左先"},{"pid":"04203e545d11d7301059f54a6d45e8f95427d091","tid":1625323,"uid":222189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:40:23.000Z","msg":"自己聽返先覺得細聲，屌<br />\n下次整大聲少少"},{"pid":"d32d3b9e9228fb39473c35aae3ea2822e1b2c30c","tid":1625323,"uid":222189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:43:11.000Z","msg":"黎緊想開始鍛鍊既朋友而係冇健身室會籍請買彈力/阻力帶/橡筋帶<br />\n唔知正式叫咩名<br />\n最好選擇長而幼，唔好覺得自己大力就買一條好粗，覺得自己細力就買一條好幼<br />\n唔同動作要用唔用既阻力，幼至粗都一定會有用<br />\n係自己許可範圍內買多幾條唔同阻力既！"},{"pid":"cda8d1aa34c10ddda534e272ef76b38352b53213","tid":1625323,"uid":222189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:51:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d2652d0f317cbf637a64e96695bd1870bcf78d","tid":1625323,"uid":45766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:53:42.000Z","msg":"推 前線個身實在太薄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6892159cb2bdab01040fad8ad1fe163360de88f4","tid":1625323,"uid":15658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164f1793558f268da3bff931d7b60d3eda0e36a8","tid":1625323,"uid":6648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:56:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f4238784412eac74665c2de5e54fc93366b7f71","tid":1625323,"uid":222189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:08:54.000Z","msg":"其實有冇人會真係睇架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人覺得太細聲 / 我講野唔清楚？"},{"pid":"8214ae7b79de8b634ed7179878f8a6f2755b49ec","tid":1625323,"uid":273854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:50:04.000Z","msg":"少上黎, 所以幫唔到手set program <br />\n但有少少意見, 樓主可以參考下<br />\n<br />\n唔應該用bodybuilding 嘅方式練<br />\n而係好似戰狼300 以實戰為目標去set program<br />\n<br />\n可以參考各地嘅軍人或警察training program<br />\n全部都唔會著重weight training. <br />\n<br />\n例如可以<br />\n1. push up<br />\n2. pull up<br />\n3. 藥球<br />\n4. rope<br />\n5. 跑樓梯 (快+跳級, 上and 落)<br />\n6. 負重跑<br />\n7. burpee<br />\n<br />\n重點係要train strength 而唔係練大隻<br />\n(消防員都有啲睇落好瘦)<br />\n所以唔似做weight training 咁<br />\n唔駛每個動作都要exhaust 晒<br />\n唔駛動作靚(唔夠力可以不停出cheat)<br />\n唔駛比rest day (即係每日都做, 最多比個weekend 去做rest)<br />\n而每組動作之間, 而每組動作之間, 係無, 或者好短嘅rest time<br />\n所有disciplined services 嘅training 都係咁<br />\n<br />\n例如做完15 下 push up<br />\n要即做15 下pull up <br />\n再做15下burpee<br />\n即黎個30 下situp<br />\n再跑返個400M<br />\n<br />\n如需要簡化版<br />\n其實可以睇返各紀律部隊入職體能考試<br />\n跟住黎做已經好夠新仔用<br />\n<br />\n實際上<br />\n如果你可以無間斷咁完成到&quot;舊&quot; 消防個體能考試<br />\n你體能一定除左機場特警同飛虎外，好過晒所以其他警犬。"},{"pid":"3b72274f0a72c0b0bc7eeebcf8b362ffb5059a85","tid":1625323,"uid":25025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:50:57.000Z","msg":"先留名，一陣睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb6f57efa99c7aad8a548cdbdde0350cb199ec8","tid":1625323,"uid":222189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8214ae7b79de8b634ed7179878f8a6f2755b49ec","tid":1625323,"uid":273854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:50:04.000Z","msg":"少上黎, 所以幫唔到手set program <br />\n但有少少意見, 樓主可以參考下<br />\n<br />\n唔應該用bodybuilding 嘅方式練<br />\n而係好似戰狼300 以實戰為目標去set program<br />\n<br />\n可以參考各地嘅軍人或警察training program<br />\n全部都唔會著重weight training. <br />\n<br />\n例如可以<br />\n1. push up<br />\n2. pull up<br />\n3. 藥球<br />\n4. rope<br />\n5. 跑樓梯 (快+跳級, 上and 落)<br />\n6. 負重跑<br />\n7. burpee<br />\n<br />\n重點係要train strength 而唔係練大隻<br />\n(消防員都有啲睇落好瘦)<br />\n所以唔似做weight training 咁<br />\n唔駛每個動作都要exhaust 晒<br />\n唔駛動作靚(唔夠力可以不停出cheat)<br />\n唔駛比rest day (即係每日都做, 最多比個weekend 去做rest)<br />\n而每組動作之間, 而每組動作之間, 係無, 或者好短嘅rest time<br />\n所有disciplined services 嘅training 都係咁<br />\n<br />\n例如做完15 下 push up<br />\n要即做15 下pull up <br />\n再做15下burpee<br />\n即黎個30 下situp<br />\n再跑返個400M<br />\n<br />\n如需要簡化版<br />\n其實可以睇返各紀律部隊入職體能考試<br />\n跟住黎做已經好夠新仔用<br />\n<br />\n實際上<br />\n如果你可以無間斷咁完成到&quot;舊&quot; 消防個體能考試<br />\n你體能一定除左機場特警同飛虎外，好過晒所以其他警犬。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:57:52.000Z","msg":"多謝呀終於有人認真比意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔會用bodybuilding既方式去講解架，我希望大家係有力量既全能鬥士<br />\nweight training只係工具，可以更快達到個目標<br />\n依家各地嘅軍人或警察裝備都已經好好<br />\n所以佢地只需要有能力帶住啲裝備走已經好足夠<br />\n我第一個PO講過，裝備愈好體能需求愈低，裝備愈低體能需求愈高<br />\n呢個係我係前線觀察同思考過既野，總之一定唔會bodybuilding式訓練<br />\n<br />\n阻力訓練都係train strength既最好訓練，當然要另外加入跑步既訓練<br />\n<br />\n我都支持訓練唔exhaust 晒，第二集既犒已經打緊<br />\n<br />\n其中一部份<br />\n「<br />\n我遲下講解動作時會推介埋果個動作大約做幾多下，多數係一個範圍<br />\n當我講要深蹲十下，唔係叫你用自身體重深蹲十下就算。<br />\n而係用一個重量係你只能夠做到11-12下去做十下<br />\n點解唔係用做到十下既重量去做十下？<br />\n因為咁樣就等同做左一次力竭訓練(指完成後無法再多做一下)<br />\n我係極唔推薦大家係每日一開始既大型複合動作就練到力竭<br />\n有兩個原因<br />\n愈接力力竭動作本身會變型，訓練既目標肌肉不勝負苛身體會自動搵其他肌肉黎幫手完成個動作<br />\n同埋<br />\n訓練一開始就力竭，果舊肌肉會細力左好多，會令當日訓練量下降<br />\n同埋<br />\n操到力竭需要更長既修復時間<br />\n」<br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打認真比意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84a6584c9d8abb96572f22ddae1f3afa4faca898","tid":1625323,"uid":158977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:11:44.000Z","msg":"聽你把聲都聞到你啲testosterone多到漏出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462c23b193faf16d99be4f0eb184f416bd01e43e","tid":1625323,"uid":222189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84a6584c9d8abb96572f22ddae1f3afa4faca898","tid":1625323,"uid":158977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:11:44.000Z","msg":"聽你把聲都聞到你啲testosterone多到漏出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9199ec067002a0f1029092bc648aea91f89b9203","tid":1625323,"uid":74244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:13:48.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n全民健身"},{"pid":"e57d5435b8faae9ec03854bfb29d88fec1384d0a","tid":1625323,"uid":89546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4574b0fe5406920f1b2bfe0c60891201d0e4267e","tid":1625323,"uid":34793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:24:16.000Z","msg":"thank you bro"},{"pid":"df4d31312fe6894cf414f3aede3de00b7162552e","tid":1625323,"uid":54471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:25:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f41357b88289cd68b4e5c8f44555fc85e93ad40d","tid":1625323,"uid":222189,"like":0,"disli