mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:00:09.000Z","msg":"唔使<br />\n可以做簡易版先 例如做唔到掌手壓 就做膝上壓先<br />\n做唔到引體上升 可以跳上去最頂再慢慢落 練negative 或者用拉力帶黎輔助做引體<br />\n好快會進步到做到完整版"},{"pid":"c791c0ae5aa21daac87a3f878c8f361ccbf3c4c5","tid":1625323,"uid":222189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b21f5a39c917e106d95d049238b24949ca642c71","tid":1625323,"uid":73004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:57:07.000Z","msg":"我想問下想練駛唔駛減左肥先？<br />\n<br />\n我試過做push up/引體上升果d都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:02:37.000Z","msg":"除非真係好肥<br />\n如果唔係減肥期間身體活動能力會低左<br />\n唔好特登諗住減肥<br />\n食健康既野，比心機鍛鍊，身體自然愈黎愈強愈黎愈好<br />\n<br />\n引體我操左1年半先做到1下..HAAAHAAA  肥底本身成95KG..<br />\n做唔到我都有方法令你訓練到，因為我地唔係徒手訓練<br />\n我地係彈力帶訓練<br />\n最簡單係公園放條彈力帶落黎吊住對腳就可以容易啲做引體<br />\n一條唔得就兩條<br />\n驚落公園做既我都已經諗好左替代動作，引體係垂直將重量拉近身體既動作<br />\n已經諗好取代訓練方法!! (不過要有彈力帶)<br />\n<br />\n懷疑自己係彈力帶打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ff9e6002c5f543dfe60aa80cf60a1058ebb279","tid":1625323,"uid":222189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:49:50.000Z","msg":"即整第三集<br />\n唔想休息<br />\n冇落前線既罪惡感好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0752a13129b3cadb694fe0b525325cfb2e2d7928","tid":1625323,"uid":222189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:57:15.000Z","msg":"拎個腳架出黎插好相機 然後佢唔小心仆親...個相機唔知冇電定壞左著唔到機<br />\n雖然只係平野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e